<div
  style="
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 30px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    color: #333333;
  "
>
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px">
    <h1 style="color: #4f46e5; margin: 0">Welcome to NestJS Blog 🎉</h1>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 16px">
    Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7">
    Thank you for signing up for <strong>NestJS Blog</strong>! We're excited
    to have you on board and can't wait for you to start exploring the
    platform.
  </p>

  <div
    style="
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    "
  >
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #111827">Your Account Details</h3>

```
<p style="margin: 8px 0">
  <strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %>
</p>

<p style="margin: 8px 0">
  <strong>Login URL:</strong><br />
  <a
    href="<%= loginUrl %>"
    style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none"
  >
    <%= loginUrl %>
  </a>
</p>
```

  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0">
    <a
      href="<%= loginUrl %>"
      style="
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
      "
    >
      Login to Your Account
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7">
    If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our
    support team.
  </p>

  <hr
    style="
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin: 30px 0;
    "
  />

  <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px">
    Best regards,<br />
    <strong>NestJS Blog Support Team</strong>
  </p>
</div>
